quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Say O Muhammad to those who have rejected Faith: \"O you infidels"
  109,2,I do not worship the idols which you worship
  109,3,"Nor do you worship Allah, Whom I worship"
  109,4,"Nor do I observe your religious rites, but I observe what accords with fact and reason and with what is logically sound"
  109,5,Nor do you observe Allah’s ordinances or such advice as Allah inclines you to propound
  109,6,You have your religion and I have mine